Name: thEiAoLoGy
About the game: An Atomic Game-Engine Generate Voxel realms using FATE Share FATEs with your friends with links that work in browsers and in game Explore curated realms from the DEMOs and Over World. Each Voxel is an Atom of a system of 256 x 256 ! Procedural generation tools for quick variation and iteration. Plot atoms using variance and flocking patterns like birds. City Physics - Explore a rainy city block with physics on the rain run off. Over World - 8 realms clustered around the center pillar. Aero - Bullet Hell where the bullets are alive. Star Voyage - Cheesy 90s Intro Space Drama Opener. Use the Weave or LISP editors bidirectionally. a Timeline that orchestrates events across a song's duration .vox support for plotting complex voxels Drag and Drop assets onto the browser to mix in Download any part of a FATE file as its original form (VOX/LISP/MP3)
